      <title>S3表示，川普社群媒體公司股價上漲給賣空者壓力</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-social-media-firms-rising-shares-pressure-short-sellers-s3-says-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[川普媒體與賣空者分析公司 S3 Partners 表示，Technology Group 正感受到該公司股價近期上漲以及借股成本上升的壓力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-social-media-firms-rising-shares-pressure-short-sellers-s3-says-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 22:09:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>川普將媒體公司的股份提高至近65%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-raises-stake-his-media-firm-nearly-65-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根據週二提交的文件，截至上週，唐納德·川普已將其在運營其社交媒體應用程式 Truth Social 的公司中的股份提高到近 65%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-raises-stake-his-media-firm-nearly-65-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:29:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IBM 贏得撤銷 BMC 價值 16 億美元的軟體合約判決</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/ibm-wins-reversal-16-billion-judgment-bmc-over-software-contract-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[聯邦上訴法院週二推翻了一項要求 IBM 向競爭對手 BMC Software 支付 16 億美元的判決，法官發現 IBM 不當地用自己的軟體取代了 AT&amp;T 的 BMC 大型主機軟體。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/ibm-wins-reversal-16-billion-judgment-bmc-over-software-contract-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 21:20:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Skyworks 預計第三季營收低於預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/skyworks-forecasts-third-quarter-revenue-below-estimates-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由於需求擔憂，蘋果供應商 Skyworks Solutions 週二預測第三季營收低於華爾街預期，因客戶難以卸載多餘庫存，導致其股價在盤後交易中下跌 6%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/skyworks-forecasts-third-quarter-revenue-below-estimates-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:58:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AHA 表示，幾乎所有美國醫院都因 Change 駭客攻擊而遭受了經濟損失</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/almost-all-us-hospitals-took-financial-hit-change-hack-aha-says-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美國醫院協會 (AHA) 的一項調查顯示，今年早些時候，聯合健康集團旗下 Change Healthcare 部門遭受網路攻擊，幾乎所有美國醫院都遭受了經濟損失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/almost-all-us-hospitals-took-financial-hit-change-hack-aha-says-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AMD AI晶片營收預期不如預期，股價暴跌7%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chipmaker-amd-beats-first-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Advanced Micro Devices 週二預測的 AI 晶片銷量未能給投資者留下深刻印象，導致其股價在盤後交易中下跌約 7%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chipmaker-amd-beats-first-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:23:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由於庫存增加，超微季度營收未達預期，股價下跌 14%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/super-micro-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-above-estimates-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人工智慧伺服器製造商超微電腦週二公佈的第三季度收入低於預期，原因是一些關鍵組件短缺以及新伺服器系列盈利能力受到質疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/super-micro-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-above-estimates-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:10:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pinterest 預測季度營收高於預期，股價飆升</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/pinterest-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-above-estimates-robust-ad-spend-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Pinterest 週二預測第二季營收高於華爾街預期，與亞馬遜和谷歌的廣告合作夥伴關係預計將帶來提振，導致其股價在盤後交易中上漲超過 16%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/pinterest-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-above-estimates-robust-ad-spend-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:08:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亞馬遜業績超乎預期，營收未達預期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/amazon-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-below-estimates-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亞馬遜週二公佈的季度業績超出了華爾街的預期，因為人們對人工智慧的興趣推動了雲端運算的成長。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/amazon-forecasts-quarterly-revenue-below-estimates-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:04:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
